data.description: Welcome to your private homestead! This 4br/1.5b is located on 5.6 acres of land. The large living room and kitchen create an open space concept with a beautiful wood burning fireplace. HVAC was installed in 2020 and hot water heater in 2021. All NEW ductwork. It has a storage building in the back and plenty of privacy. The house needs a little work but has had a few renovations in the past month. THIS IS A MOTIVATED SELLER!
